New Records: Anthony Edwards scored a game-high 33 points, eight rebounds, and six assists; Mike Conley had 14 points and 11 assists
Key Match Events: Minnesota Timberwolves rally from a 13-point deficit; Anthony Edwards' two key three-pointers in the fourth quarter; a 12-0 run by the Timberwolves to take the lead
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Bulls went 10 for 17 from three-point range in the first half; the Timberwolves shot 70.8 per cent from the field in the fourth quarter
